WebKit: Shipped/Shipping (&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://webkit.org/blog/16301/webkit-features-in-safari-18-2"&gt;https://webkit.org/blog/16301/webkit-features-in-safari-18-2&lt;/a&gt;)
Web developers: Positive This is a highly requested feature to prevent the need to uniquely identify each participating view transition element.
