/None/

*Goals for experimentation*

&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;The noise added means that the 'confidence' field isn’t immediately 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;useful to developers. Developers can collect this field in their Real 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;User Monitoring (RUM) data and with enough records, correct the data 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;to &quot;eliminate the noise&quot;. One of the objectives of the experiment is 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;to confirm developers are successfully able to do that. We're also 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;interested in feedback about the API shape and ease of use.
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;


