&gt;&gt; They are defined in
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/web_tests/external/wpt/mediacapture-record/MediaRecorder-canvas-media-source.https.html;l=16"&gt;https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/web_tests/external/wpt/mediacapture-record/MediaRecorder-canvas-media-source.https.html;l=16&lt;/a&gt;
